A cluster can be imported using the `id` of the resource, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import yandex:index/mdbElasticsearchCluster:MdbElasticsearchCluster foo cluster_id
```

yandex:index/mdbKafkaCluster:MdbKafkaClu.description:
Manages a Kafka cluster within the Yandex.Cloud. For more information, see
[the official documentation](https://cloud.yandex.com/docs/managed-kafka/concepts).

## Example Usage

Example of creating a Single Node Kafka.

